<collectingCountry box="[362,499,333,359]" name="Madagascar" pageId="19" pageNumber="20">Madagascar</collectingCountry>
. In forested areas of the south and northwest, at lower altitudes (
<quantity box="[1220,1335,333,359]" metricMagnitude="2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.15" metricValueMax="3.6" metricValueMin="0.7" pageId="19" pageNumber="20" unit="m" value="215.0" valueMax="360.0" valueMin="70.0">
70 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1250,1264,333,359]" pageId="19" pageNumber="20">–</emphasis>
360 m
